Package: ucode-quickjs
Section: interpreters
Priority: optional
Depends:  quickjs, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: ucode JavaScript interpreter with QuickJS backend
 ucode is a JavaScript-like scripting language with a QuickJS backend.
 This package provides the ucode interpreter and runtime libraries.
 .
 This package contains the runtime components.

Package: libucode-quickjs-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Depends: ucode-quickjs (= ${version})
Description: ucode JavaScript interpreter - development files
 ucode is a JavaScript-like scripting language with a QuickJS backend.
 .
 This package contains the development headers and libraries needed
 to build applications using ucode.
